Daniel, it is my honor to inform
you that you have been awarded

10
00:00:23,118 --> 00:00:27,891
this year's Davenport Prize
for exploration in science.

11
00:00:27,892 --> 00:00:30,119
I.. I swear, I knew nothing about this.

12
00:00:30,120 --> 00:00:33,552
And, as I'm sure you are aware,
this award is not just about

13
00:00:33,553 --> 00:00:36,625
the laurels you bring to
yourself and the university.

14
00:00:36,626 --> 00:00:40,749
It's also about the $50,000
check that goes along with it.

15
00:00:40,750 --> 00:00:42,419
Woo!

16
00:00:42,420 --> 00:00:45,180
To Daniel Pierce.

17
